Package org.forgerock.openidm.smartevent

Class Name

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.smartevent.Name
public class Name extends Object
Represents the name and additional configuration for an event type Allows callers to pre-construct, parse event hierarchies and set additional configuration by declaring the Names outside of the publishing of the events The fluent API allows for easier set-up directly in the declaration example: public static final Name MY_EVENT = Name.get("internal/myevent").setTags(new String[] {MONITOR, APP_EVENT}).setXyz("dummy")
